Pet Haven Hub - New Adoption Request
=====================================

NEW REQUEST REQUIRES REVIEW

A new adoption request has been submitted and requires your review.

PET INFORMATION
---------------
Name: <%= @pet&.name || 'Unknown Pet' %>
Type: <%= @pet&.pet_type&.capitalize || 'Unknown' %>
<% if @pet&.breed.present? %>Breed: <%= @pet.breed %><% end %>
<% if @pet&.age.present? %>Age: <%= @pet.age %> years old<% end %>

REQUESTER DETAILS
-----------------
Name: <%= @user&.name || 'Unknown User' %>
Email: <%= @user&.email || 'No email provided' %>
<% if @request&.phone_number.present? %>Phone: <%= @request.phone_number %><% end %>

REQUEST DETAILS
---------------
Request Type: <%= @request&.request_type&.capitalize || 'Adoption' %>
Submitted: <%= @request&.created_at&.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') || 'Unknown' %>
<% if @request&.house_type.present? %>Housing Type: <%= @request.house_type.humanize %><% end %>
Status: <%= @request&.status&.humanize || 'Open' %>

<% if @request&.reason.present? %>
REASON FOR ADOPTION
-------------------
<%= @request.reason %>
<% end %>

ACTION REQUIRED
---------------
Review this request in the admin dashboard:
<%= @admin_dashboard_url %>

